<P>WHere <HI>Vertue</HI> is sowne in a noble Seed-plot,<NOTE PLACE="marg"><HI>Vertue</HI> or <HI>vice</HI> whethersoe|uer takes hold first, re|taines a dee|per impressi|on in <HI>honour,</HI> than any low|er subiect.</NOTE>
