a poore habit neuer retaines that maiesty, which it
displayes in a richer ro<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">be. Is it so? Reflect then vp|on
your selues; if vice seeme so specious, what will
<HI>vertue</HI> do. (Though all your <HI>vertues</HI> be but indeed spe|cious
<HI>vices.</HI>) Beleeue it, if you cherish <HI>vertue</HI> in your
