<P>IT is vsually obseru'd, that <HI>Hawkes</HI> of one <HI>Ayrie,</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg">That vertue may receiue the first im|pression by meanes of an in-bred noble <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="2 letters">sposition, seco<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">ded by helps of Edu|cation.</NOTE>
are not of one <HI>nature;</HI> Some are more mettall'd,
