<P>Industrious were their hands in labouring, and
bounteous were they in bestowing. A natiue com|passion
lodged in their hearts, which they expressed
in their charitable workes. Hospitality to the stran|ger
and needy beggar, was their highest <HI>honour.</HI> Suf|fer
