fare</HI> delight you? Consider how it is the grea|test
misery to pamper that delicately, or cherish it
with delicacy that is your mortall and profest ene|my
Doe <HI>wanton Consort&punc;</HI> worke on your fancy? Cure
betime, this dangerous phrenzy. Auert your <HI>eye,</HI> lest
