Shake off this naturall du<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">nesse, and inflame your af|fections
with a Diuine feruentnesse. You haue hi|therto
beene slow in doing good, shew that in do|ing
ill. Meane time, with the wings of holy and
