cur<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">e God, their Neighbors, and themselues in their
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">duersity: Whence that D<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">uine and deuout Father
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">aith: <Q>In affliction the wicked detest God, and<NOTE PLACE="marg">Aug. lib. 1. de Ciuit. Dei.</NOTE>
