draw you nearer heauen. If you feare at any
time to wander, <HI>Religious feare</HI> will bee your <HI>Condu|ctor.</HI>
If you doubt the issue of your Encounter, <HI>sted|fast
patience</HI> will be your <HI>Encourager.</HI> If you distrust
