<P>VVHat remaines then,<NOTE PLACE="marg">Vertue <HI>re|duc'd to</HI> b<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">|bit, <HI>aspires to</HI> perfection&punc;</NOTE> to perfit this absolute
Master-piece of <HI>honour;</HI> but that yee re|duce
