Let <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">our <HI>Virgin-Lamps</HI> be fed with the <HI>Oyle</HI> of
<HI>Charity.</HI> Be ready before the <HI>Bridegroome</HI> call you;
